In [20]:
### Month Loop
for m in np.unique(LuckyMRC['MTH']):
    LuckyMRC_Month = LuckyMRC.query('MTH == @m')
    from_portion = LuckyMRC_Month.query('fromPP in @lucky_top_PP').shape[0]/LuckyMRC_Month.shape[0]
    to_portion = LuckyMRC_Month.query('toPP in @lucky_top_PP').shape[0]/LuckyMRC_Month.shape[0]

    print(f'\n\nMonth: {m}')
    print(f'from: {from_portion:0.2%}')
    print(f'to: {to_portion:0.2%}')

    lucky_movement_month = LuckyMRC_Month.query('fromPP in @lucky_top_PP and toPP in @lucky_top_PP')[['fromPP', 'toPP']].value_counts().rename('count').reset_index()
    lucky_movement_month = lucky_movement_month.query('fromPP != toPP').sort_values(by=['fromPP', 'toPP'])

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 10))
    g = sns.scatterplot(data=lucky_movement_month, sizes=(1, 500), x='fromPP', y='toPP', hue='count', size='count', s=500, ax=ax)
    g.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 0.8), ncol=1)
    plt.show()

### Month Loop
for m in np.unique(LuckyMRC['MTH']):
    LuckyMRC_month = LuckyMRC.query('MTH == @m')

    lucky_movement_month = LuckyMRC_month[['fromPP', 'toPP']].value_counts().rename('count').reset_index()
    lucky_movement_month = lucky_movement_month.query('fromPP != toPP').sort_values(by=['fromPP', 'toPP'])

    print(f'\n\nMonth: {m}')

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 10))
    g = sns.scatterplot(data=lucky_movement_month, sizes=(1, 500), x='fromPP', y='toPP', hue='count', size='count', s=500, ax=ax)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    g.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 0.8), ncol=1)
    plt.show();

In [37]:
### Month Loop
for m in np.unique(BellMRC['MTH']):
    BellMRC_Month = BellMRC.query('MTH == @m')

    bell_movement_month = BellMRC_Month[['fromPP', 'toPP']].value_counts().rename('count').reset_index()
    bell_movement_month = bell_movement_month.query('fromPP != toPP').sort_values(by=['fromPP', 'toPP'])

    movement_cutoff = 0.001*bell_movement_month['count'].sum()
    bell_movement_month_sub = bell_movement_month.query('count >= @movement_cutoff')
    
    print(f'\n\nMonth: {m}')
    print(f'movement cutoff: {movement_cutoff:0.2f}')

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(30, 10))
    g = sns.scatterplot(data=bell_movement_month_sub, sizes=(1, 500), x='fromPP', y='toPP', hue='count', size='count', s=500, ax=ax)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    g.legend(loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 0.8), ncol=1)
    plt.show();
